name: Leeron Shalev on Github
body:
## Welcome to my git github page !!1
There is not much here at the moment. 
I basically created this page so I can host the [live demo](bla) of my interactive HTML5 javascript [mandelbrot set](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mandelbrot_set) implementation. 
I created this implementation as part of a [github project](https://github.com/danyshaanan/mandelbrot) I colaborate on with my friend and coworker [https://github.com/danyshaanan](Dany Shaanan).
